<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạlly bạlkẖṭyẗ mḥny yạlly
 mgẖlwb mn ʿạdạtk
 yạlly ʿbd wsydh qạsy wmnyth ydmr ḥyạtk
 ạ̉gẖlb ạlsẖyṭạn wạhrb llmsyḥ wạtrk fsạdk
 ạlqrạr- dạ ạlmsyḥ qạỷd fy mwkb ạlnṣrẗ
 ạlkbyr
