 wsmr ạlṣk fy mkạnh bmsạmyr
 bʿd mwth wbqyạmth gẖlb ạlʿdw wdyạnth
 wḥrr ạlạ̉sry̱ mn ạlsjn ạlmryr
 2- yạlly ṭwl ạlywm btsẖky mn ʿdwk ʿmạlyq</lyrics>
